title: Athletics at the West African University Games
text:
The <a href="sport%20of%20athletics">athletics</a> competition at the <a href="West%20African%20University%20Games">West African University Games</a> has featured at all editions since the first in 1965. the most recent edition of the competition was the 14th, held in 2018.
A limited number of athletics medallists are known from the competitions.
